description: Deletes a given Timestream table. This is an irreversible operation. After a Timestream database table is deleted, the time-series data stored in the table cannot be recovered. See code sample for details.

parameters.name: DatabaseName
parameters.description: The name of the database where the Timestream database is to be deleted.

parameters.name: TableName
parameters.description: The name of the Timestream table to be deleted.
